---
/**
 * 陶瓷技艺项目页
 * 展示陶瓷历史源流、代表作品、制作流程（AI_Animation动画）、文化内涵
 * 联动入口：摄影/3D/视频
 */
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="陶瓷技艺 - 非遗传承">
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Hero 区：标题与简介 -->
  <section class="craft-hero" id="top">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="craft-eyebrow">非遗 · 陶瓷烧造技艺</p>
      <h1 class="craft-title">陶瓷技艺</h1>
      <p class="craft-subtitle">取大地之土，经火炼成器</p>
      <p class="craft-intro">
        从新石器时代的彩陶盆，到唐宋的青瓷碗，再到明清的青花瓶。<br />
        每一件瓷器都是"土与火的对话"，凝结着千年的匠心与智慧。
      </p>
      <a href="#history" class="scroll-hint" aria-label="向下浏览">
        <span>向下浏览</span>
        <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 历史源流 -->
  <section class="section craft-section" id="history">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">历史源流</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">八千年窑火不熄，泥土涅槃成器</p>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-era">新石器时代</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>陶器起源</h3>
            <p>约一万年前，先民开始用黏土制作简单陶器。河姆渡遗址出土的陶器，标志着陶瓷艺术的最初起源。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-era">商周时期</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>原始青瓷</h3>
            <p>出现了原始青瓷，被认为是世界上最早的瓷器。东汉时期，绍兴上虞第一次制成了成熟的瓷器。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-era">唐宋时期</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>南青北白</h3>
            <p>形成南青北白的制瓷格局——越窑青瓷、邢窑白瓷。宋元时期进入繁荣，形成"五大名窑"：汝、官、哥、钧、定。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-era">元明清时期</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>景德镇鼎盛</h3>
            <p>景德镇成为御窑，青花瓷、彩绘瓷盛极一时。明朝的釉里红、成化斗彩，清朝的郎窑红、粉彩，皆为传世珍品。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 代表作品 -->
  <section class="section craft-section section-alt" id="works">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">代表作品</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">泥土与火焰凝结的传世之美</p>

      <div class="works-grid">
        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="work-image work-image-1" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="work-placeholder">青花</span>
          </div>
          <div class="work-body">
            <h3>元青花四爱图梅瓶</h3>
            <p class="work-era">元代 · 景德镇窑</p>
            <p>青花瓷以钴料绘纹，白底蓝花，淡雅色调契合文人意境。此瓶是最早的青花完整器之一。</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="work-image work-image-2" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="work-placeholder">汝窑</span>
          </div>
          <div class="work-body">
            <h3>汝窑天青釉</h3>
            <p class="work-era">宋代 · 五大名窑之首</p>
            <p>汝瓷擅用玛瑙入釉，釉色素静典雅，"青如天、面如玉、质如乳、声如磬"，烧制难度极高。</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="work-image work-image-3" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="work-placeholder">粉彩</span>
          </div>
          <div class="work-body">
            <h3>清乾隆粉彩百花尊</h3>
            <p class="work-era">清代 · 景德镇御窑</p>
            <p>粉彩受西洋珐琅影响，色调柔软粉化，百花满地，富丽堂皇，代表清代制瓷工艺巅峰。</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="work-image work-image-4" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="work-placeholder">建盏</span>
          </div>
          <div class="work-body">
            <h3>建窑建盏</h3>
            <p class="work-era">宋代 · 福建建阳</p>
            <p>黑釉瓷的杰出代表，结晶釉因烧成技术不同产生兔毫、油滴等釉色，为宋代皇室御用茶器。</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 制作流程（AI_Animation 动画） -->
  <section class="section craft-section" id="process">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">制作流程</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">"共计一坯之力，过手七十二，方克成器" ——《天工开物》</p>

      <div class="animation-wrapper">
        <iframe
          class="process-animation"
          src={Astro.resolve("/animations/ceramic-process.html")}
          title="陶瓷制作流程动画"
          loading="lazy"
          frameborder="0"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="process-step-card">
          <span class="step-number">01</span>
          <h3>揉泥</h3>
          <p>精选高岭土，反复揉炼排出气泡，使泥性均匀柔韧。陈腐越久，柔韧性越好，拉坯时不易开裂。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step-card">
          <span class="step-number">02</span>
          <h3>拉坯</h3>
          <p>泥团置于轮盘，双手提拉，"三提三压"塑出器型。力度要匀，如"抱婴儿"般顺泥之脾气。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step-card">
          <span class="step-number">03</span>
          <h3>修坯</h3>
          <p>以竹刀修整厚薄曲直，景德镇薄胎瓷厚度仅0.5毫米，透光可见指影，全凭手感"摸到泥的骨头"。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step-card">
          <span class="step-number">04</span>
          <h3>上釉</h3>
          <p>石英、长石制成的釉料覆盖坯面，既保护瓷体，又赋予玻璃般光泽，更具美感。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step-card">
          <span class="step-number">05</span>
          <h3>烧窑</h3>
          <p>千度高温，泥土涅槃。窑火之中，釉色流转，化而为瓷，光润如玉。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 文化内涵 -->
  <section class="section craft-section section-alt" id="culture">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">文化内涵</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">瓷以载道，器以传情</p>

      <div class="culture-grid">
        <div class="culture-card">
          <div class="culture-icon" aria-hidden="true">土</div>
          <h3>水土之合</h3>
          <p>陶瓷以水土为基，水润土性，土承水形。水土交融间，化作万千器型，体现"道法自然"的哲学。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="culture-card">
          <div class="culture-icon" aria-hidden="true">火</div>
          <h3>窑火涅槃</h3>
          <p>千度高温，泥土化瓷。火的淬炼，象征匠人坚守与蜕变，"浴火重生"的东方智慧。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="culture-card">
          <div class="culture-icon" aria-hidden="true">雅</div>
          <h3>文人意境</h3>
          <p>青花的淡雅、汝窑的天青，契合中国文人山水意境。瓷以载道，承载东方审美与精神追求。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="culture-card">
          <div class="culture-icon" aria-hidden="true">通</div>
          <h3>文明互鉴</h3>
          <p>瓷器沿丝绸之路远销海外，"China"即瓷之意。一抹青花，连接东西，成为中华文明的世界名片。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 联动入口 -->
  <section class="section craft-section" id="explore">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">深度探索</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">从不同维度，继续走进陶瓷世界</p>

      <div class="explore-grid">
        <a href={Astro.resolve("/gallery?category=ceramic")} class="explore-card">
          <div class="explore-icon" aria-hidden="true">摄影</div>
          <h3>陶瓷摄影</h3>
          <p>高清影像记录陶瓷之美，从器型到釉色，尽收眼底。</p>
          <span class="explore-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href={Astro.resolve("/model?category=ceramic")} class="explore-card">
          <div class="explore-icon" aria-hidden="true">3D</div>
          <h3>3D 模型</h3>
          <p>360度旋转观赏，细品陶瓷的每一处曲线与纹饰。</p>
          <span class="explore-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href={Astro.resolve("/video?category=ceramic")} class="explore-card">
          <div class="explore-icon" aria-hidden="true">视频</div>
          <h3>科普视频</h3>
          <p>影像记录匠人手作，听他们讲述泥土与火焰的故事。</p>
          <span class="explore-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero 区 */
  .craft-hero {
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: var(--nav-height);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.15) 0%, rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8) 100%);
    position: relative;
  }

  .craft-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .craft-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .craft-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .craft-intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.8);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .scroll-hint:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .scroll-hint .arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(8px); }
  }

  /* 通用 section */
  .craft-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
  }

  .section-alt {
    background-color: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.5);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  /* 时间线 */
  .timeline {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-accent), transparent);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.2);
  }

  .timeline-era {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* 代表作品 */
  .works-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .work-card {
    background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .work-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .work-image {
    height: 200px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.4);
  }

  .work-image-1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f, #2c5282); }
  .work-image-2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a5c6a, #7a8a95); }
  .work-image-3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b4a6f, #c4719c); }
  .work-image-4 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d2d2d, #4a4a4a); }

  .work-body {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .work-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .work-era {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .work-body p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* 动画区 */
  .animation-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-2xl);
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #1A1A2E;
  }

  .process-animation {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  /* 工序卡片 */
  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .process-step-card {
    background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.4);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  }

  .step-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .process-step-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .process-step-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* 文化内涵 */
  .culture-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .culture-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.15);
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .culture-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .culture-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-md);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .culture-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .culture-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  /* 联动入口 */
  .explore-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .explore-card {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .explore-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .explore-icon {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--spacing-xs) var(--spacing-md);
    background: rgba(196, 163, 90, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .explore-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .explore-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .explore-arrow {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .explore-card:hover .explore-arrow {
    transform: translateX(8px);
  }

  /* 响应式 */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .craft-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
